{"tid":998143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好難得會對一個人動心，但佢原來拍左拖十年。","createTime":"2019-01-27T17:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T02:03:07.000Z","uid":7678,"like":8,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3b2202c5f73c42b968b95f2b270472dc8638e6","tid":998143,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"對上一次真係對一個人動心係2012 年仲讀緊大學既事。（住同一間hall 日對夜對，日久生情但無一齊過）<br />\n結果佢2018 年結婚生仔，我自問唔係君子，但都可以真心為佢高興，鄧佢開心，我就知道自己當初對佢係真心。<br />\n<br />\n2012-18 年間斷斷續續都拍過唔少次拖對另一半都唔會有咁強烈既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n由2018 年中開始經常落吧，半年來帶過十幾個人返屋企到天光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無諗過2019 年既1 月，呢種久違7 年既強烈感覺來第二次。<br />\n今次竟然係只係一星期前係酒吧識到既你，同你kiss 完，交換完contact 之後發現自己對你真係有好強烈既感覺。<br />\n從來唔相信一見鍾情呢回事。<br />\n<br />\n同你食飯真係好開心。你好靚，而且原來你唔係咁cool， 都有好多野講。但原來你有個拍左拖兼同居10 年既男朋友。好多謝你無選擇講大話呃我話自己單身。我問你有無男朋友多謝你大方承認你果個10 年同居男友既存在。<br />\n<br />\n但我已經唔識點再處理。自問平日工作再chur 都游刃有餘，唯獨是你我唔識點面對。"},{"pid":"06ede9568a8941776bf849ec14f4a39134c840ae","tid":998143,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"好掛住你，經常會好奇你做緊乜，過得開唔開心"},{"pid":"cd901847d906eb6b68cdf0b6d6dc3df8400d2663","tid":998143,"uid":7678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"到底我應該點做"},{"pid":"a29256ac40476425938b6ab419dd0827ca34c1fc","tid":998143,"uid":169676,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"酒吧識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5615bf76d2016e7ce15e3f261b461cd31120d743","tid":998143,"uid":162713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T19:12:55.000Z","msg":"同佢發展做sp算啦<br />\n<br />\n夜場講真愛 只會變悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a8b26355adf257ff59ff95f7747dbf3f40588f","tid":998143,"uid":231943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"我都好耐冇試過咁心動 直情小鹿亂撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我知我地冇可能 我不停同自己講 冇可能<br />\n唔該唔好鍾意人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d829310e1b4fa2ebfecda061e0a26cbb044c7371","tid":998143,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29256ac40476425938b6ab419dd0827ca34c1fc","tid":998143,"uid":169676,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"酒吧識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:12:19.000Z","msg":"觀場無⋯"},{"pid":"bed0dfc078a3eae719d40fb8b04cde099097d01f","tid":998143,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"好mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f88734c5ee4a865f43c23207e117e972aa7bd6b","tid":998143,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:23:33.000Z","msg":"酒吧帶女番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06936e7bb86947289f7d2659ab08ba374cac468","tid":998143,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"bar識, 兩邊都係狗男女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}